text: Kuganakbash () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kuganakbashevsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 835 as of 2010. There are 10 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Sterlibashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Kuganakbash
